newsitem.title: USA: CBOT rice ends mixed, commercial buying cited.
newsitem.headline: CBOT rice ends mixed, commercial buying cited.

text.p: CBOT rice futures closed mixed but mostly firm with steady commercial buying noted, traders said.
"We continue to get good commercial buying and funds were buyers," a trader said.
Traders said demand for rice remains consistent but there was producer selling during rallies which checked advances.
Rice closed one cent per cwt lower to four higher, with November down one at $10.40 per cwt.
Rice futures volume was estimated at 200 contracts, below the 891 reported traded Friday, according to the CBOT.
